description: Partial demolition and redevelopment for ten storey buildings for mixed use purposes comprising 261 residential units (Class C3), office (Class B1), retail (Class A1), financial and professional services (Class A2), restaurant (Class A3) and community/health uses; creation of new public open space; new vehicular and pedestrian accesses; works to the public highway; basement car and cycle parking; associated works including landscaping, servicing areas and plant; retention and repair of existing chapel, No.10 Mortimer Street and Nassau Street facades.
